  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds:
    - rid: 4444056884916519031
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_002
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: You step into your mentor's office and instantly spot an old floor-to-ceiling
          bookcase packed with books in all the languages this world speaks.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_003
    - rid: 4444056884916519032
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_003
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Before you get a chance to study it, Shinrai invites you to take a
          seat.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_024
    - rid: 4444056884916519035
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_004
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Greetings, scholar. I am pleased to welcome you to the Order of Labyrinth.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056884916519036
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_005
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'A faculty renowned for its thinkers and strategists, we take pride
          in our academic achievements and the foresight that we provide to the academy. '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_006
    - rid: 4444056884916519038
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_006
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: You look at your mentor. He is serious and distant, but there's a hint
          of pride in his voice.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_007
    - rid: 4444056884916519040
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_007
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: You
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: No wonder. Shinrai puts a lot of his time into making sure the faculty
          stays at the top of Chronosoul's academic ratings.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_008
    - rid: 4444056884916519041
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_008
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Do you have any questions you would like to ask? Now is the perfect
          time to do so.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_009
    - rid: 4444056884916519042
      type: {class: VNChoiceStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_009
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        options:
        - text: Ask about the faculty
          nextStepId: step_018
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
        - text: Ask about Shinrai
          nextStepId: step_010
          kind: 0
          premiumPrice: 0
          effects: []
    - rid: 4444056884916519043
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_018
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: You
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Can you tell me more about being a student of the Order of Labyrinth?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_019
    - rid: 4444056884916519045
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_019
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'Shinrai gives you a subtle nod of approval. '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056884916519046
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_020
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Here at the Order of Labyrinth, we value logic and discipline above
          all.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056884916519047
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_021
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: If you wish to excel, you must work diligently whilst ensuring you
          have sufficient time to rest.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056884916519048
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_022
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'Shinrai furrows his brow in disapproval. '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056884916519049
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_023
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: In other words, I shall NOT have students exhaust themselves in pursuit
          of their ambitions.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_016
    - rid: 4444056884916519055
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_010
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: You
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Can you tell me a bit more about working with you?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056884916519056
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_011
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: Shinrai raises an eyebrow. Did he not expect you to ask that?
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_012
    - rid: 4444056884916519058
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_012
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'It is rarely that I am asked this question. '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_013
    - rid: 4444056884916519059
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_013
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: 'Well, I suppose I have to warn you. '
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_014
    - rid: 4444056884916519060
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_014
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: I will ask much of you, but I will do so for your own benefit, as it
          is my duty to bring forth your potential.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_015
    - rid: 4444056884916519061
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_015
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: Shinrai
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: I hope I have made myself clear.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: 
    - rid: 4444056884916519062
      type: {class: VNLineStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_016
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        speakerId: 
        pose: 0
        emotion: 0
        sfxId: 
        text: You nod mulling over Shinrai's words.
        addToLog: 1
        nextStepId: step_017
    - rid: 4444056884916519064
      type: {class: VNCommandStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_024
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        command:
          rid: 4444056884916519069
        nextStepId: step_004
    - rid: 4444056884916519067
      type: {class: VNCommandStep, ns: VN, asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        id: step_001
        label: 
        disableSkip: 0
        stopAuto: 0
        command:
          rid: 4444056884916519068
        nextStepId: step_002
